KieraDialogue: ^KIERA: How do you do! Hope you are enjoying yourselves!
^CIELLE: Yes we’re doing just fine! Everyone’s really nice around here!
^COSMO: Say, that pathway right there that’s blocked off... Where does it lead to?
^KIERA: Oh! That path there leads to the outskirts of this land! Us Calmaaj came down that way when we were migrating from up north.
TheRest: ^KIERA: Yeah! We’re constantly moving to the warmest areas that allow our produce to grow to its full potential!
^COSMO: Oh that’s neat. I still don’t get why they’re blocking the path though...
^KIERA: Yeah... they’re in a pretty inconvenient spot... But I suppose it's alright!
^KIERA: We won’t be needing to leave the Aster market grounds for a few more days anyways!
^CIELLE: Yeah! This place is so nice anyways why would anyone want to leave?!
^KIERA: Very true! Well, I won't hold you guys up for much longer! Go on and enjoy the festivities!
